content: I don't have a presence on TikTok or YouTube, but I can provide you with data for the other platforms. On Facebook, I've shared two book reviews and received 15 likes and 5 comments on them. On Twitter, I've tweeted 10 times, receiving 50 likes and 20 replies. On LinkedIn, I've posted two articles on the latest digital marketing trends and received 20 likes and 5 comments on them. I'm also part of a WhatsApp group with 10 members, but I'm not sure how to measure engagement there.
